{"id": 980, "genre": 1001, "title": "有哪些公众号你曾经爱看但现在被你抛弃了？", "description": "所以究竟该怪见异思迁的我还是越来越烦人的公众号？（题图来自：Roman Muradov）", "record_count": 5414, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183758oOdHAJBLFZIv9qyl.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-06T11:26:30Z", "options": [{"id": 74496, "content": "从前写干货，后来卖广告的都被我抛弃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 74497, "content": "咪蒙 看两篇觉得清新脱俗 看20篇觉得太世俗", "image": null, "praise_count": 230, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597648}, {"id": 80641, "content": "扒一些奇葩事件的八卦号", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617678}, {"id": 74498, "content": "关八", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 67504}, {"id": 74754, "content": "大学生励志网     过了这个年龄段就不想看了，突然发现说来说去就这几样东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299470}, {"id": 74499, "content": "鬼脚七", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597659}, {"id": 81923, "content": "同道大叔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622537}, {"id": 74501, "content": "为各种打折而加的公众号！", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259532}, {"id": 75013, "content": "90斤刚刚好，以前想着激励自己减肥后来发现推手越来越多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599539}, {"id": 74503, "content": "阿富汗奸细和反常", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588611}, {"id": 75015, "content": "改变自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98189}, {"id": 74504, "content": "自从发现各种强硬劣质的广告后就都不看了", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568205}, {"id": 74505, "content": "严肃八卦，硬扭价值观", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151325}, {"id": 74506, "content": "各种健身号 自己不动有什么卵